            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000920",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-f09fcd twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-6b4cd0\"><h4 style=\"\">Section 5.  General Information About Project Gutenberg-tm electronic\nworks.</h4></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000921": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000921",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-f09fcd twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-6b4cd0\"><p>Professor Michael S. Hart was the originator of the Project Gutenberg-tm\nconcept of a library of electronic works that could be freely shared\nwith anyone.  For thirty years, he produced and distributed Project\nGutenberg-tm eBooks with only a loose network of volunteer support.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000922": {
            "role": "text",
            "title": "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000922",
            "type": "text/vnd.twpub",
            "text": "<div class=\"twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-f09fcd twpub-e5bfd381858195d5-6b4cd0\"><p style=\"\">Project Gutenberg-tm eBooks are often created from several printed\neditions, all of which are confirmed as Public Domain in the U.S.\nunless a copyright notice is included.  Thus, we do not necessarily\nkeep eBooks in compliance with any particular paper edition.</p></div>"
        },
        "$:/plugins/twpub/e5bfd381858195d5/text/000000923": {
